%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20UP%20Shocker%2C%202%20Boys%20Forced%20To%20Drink%20Urine%2C%20Tortured%20With%20Chillies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20minor%20boys%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Siddharthnagar%20district%20were%20made%20to%20drink%20urine%2C%20green%20chillies%20rubbed%20in%20their%20anus%2C%20and%20forcibly%20given%20some%20unidentifiable%20injections%20on%20suspicion%20of%20theft.%20The%20victims%20are%2010%20and%2015-year-old%20boys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHorrifying%20videos%20of%20the%20assault%20showed%20the%20boys%20made%20to%20eat%20green%20chillies%2C%20and%20gulp%20it%20down%20with%20urine%20filled%20in%20a%20bottle.%20A%20group%20of%20men%20could%20be%20heard%20abusing%20them%20and%20threatening%20to%20beat%20them%20up%20if%20they%20didn't%20go%20through%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goons%20allegedly%20caught%20the%20boys%20and%20tied%20them%20up%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20stealing%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20disturbing%20video%20shows%20the%20boys%20lying%20face%20down%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20their%20hands%20tied%20behind%20their%20backs%20and%20trousers%20pulled%20down%2C%20while%20a%20man%20rubs%20and%20shoves%20green%20chillies%20in%20their%20anus.%20The%20boys%2C%20who%20were%20screaming%20in%20pain%2C%20are%20then%20also%20injected%20with%20a%20yellow%20coloured%20liquid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20shot%20on%20August%204%2C%20is%20from%20Arshan%20Chicken%20Shop%20near%20Konkati%20Chauraha%20of%20Pathra%20Bazaar%20police%20station%20area%20of%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20took%20immediate%20cognizance%20of%20the%20video%20%26quot%3Bof%20objectionable%20act%20against%20two%20children%26quot%3B%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20law.%20They%20have%20identified%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20assault%2C%20and%20six%20of%20them%20have%20been%20detained%2C%20the%20district's%20Additional%20Sup