n%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20goes%20against%20the%20big%20picture%20of%20Sino-Russian%20friendship%20and%20the%20growing%20trend%20of%20friendly%20people-to-people%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standoff%20comes%20after%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20had%20last%20year%20proclaimed%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cno%20limits%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20friendship%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20China%20has%20refused%20to%20condemn%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20the%20countries%20have%20not%20seen%20a%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20now%2C%20China%20has%20demanded%20answers%20from%20Russia%20on%20this%20incident.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20report%20about%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20language%20used%20in%20the%20Chinese%20embassy%E2%80%99s%20post%20is%20more%20aligned%20with%20what%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20diplomats%20reserve%20for%20protests%20against%20Western%20nations.%20The%20post%20demanded%20Russia%20explain%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20take%20active%20measures%20to%20eliminate%20the%20bad%20influence%2C%20and%20ensure%20that%20similar%20incidents%20will%20not%20recur%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20statement%20posted%20on%20WeChat%20was%20also%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20Russia%20needed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cconduct%20a%20further%20investigation%20into%20the%20excessive%20law%20enforcement%20activities%20by%20border%20guards%20and%20provide%20the%20Chinese%20side%20a%20satisfactory%20answer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691310614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3