ing%20attack%20on%20the%20Opposition%20at%20Railways'%20mega%20revamp%20event%2C%C2%A0saying%20that%20it%20is%20time%20for%20%26quot%3Bcorruption%2C%20dynasty%2C%20and%20appeasement%20to%20quit%20India.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BInspired%20by%20Quit%20India%20Movement%2C%20entire%20country%20is%20now%20saying%20corruption%2C%20dynasty%2C%20appeasement%20should%20quit%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20event%20virtually%20after%20laying%20the%20foundation%20for%20redevelopment%20of%20508%20railway%20stations%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20playing%20%26quot%3Bnegative%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20alleged%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Opposition%20is%20working%20on%20a%20principle%20that%20%26quot%3Bneither%20will%20they%20work%20nor%20let%20others%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRising%20above%20negative%20politics%2C%20we%20are%20moving%20on%20path%20of%20positive%20politics%20in%20mission%20mode%2C%20giving%20priority%20to%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20today%2C%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20on%20India.%20%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20which%20is%20heading%20towards%20the%20goal%20of%20being%20developed%2C%20is%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Amrit%20Kaal.%20There%20is%20new%20energy%2C%20new%20inspiration%20and%20new%20resolutions%20and%20in%20this%20spirit%2C%20a%20new%20chapter%20is%20beginning%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20Railways%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redevelopment%20of%20508%20railway%20stations%20is%20being%20carried%20out%20under%20the%20'Amrit%20Bharat%20Station%20Scheme'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20will%20provide%20modern%20passenger%20amenities%20along%20with%20ensuring%20well-designed%20traffic%20circulation%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A