e%20motion%20tabled%20by%20the%20opposition%20against%20Modi%2C%20and%20to%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20push%20to%20pass%20the%20Delhi%20services%20bill%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Odisha%20patriarch%20has%20given%20yet%20more%20proof%20of%20the%20political%20pragmatism%20that%20his%20party%20regularly%20practises%20to%20near%20perfection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20to%20be%20ideologically%20neutral%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20always%20been%20a%20shrewd%20political%20operator.%20And%20in%20rallying%20behind%20Modi%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Parliament%20less%20than%20a%20year%20ahead%20of%20the%20next%20general%20elections%2C%20he%20has%20simply%20ensured%20that%20his%20long%20uninterrupted%20reign%20as%20the%20Odisha%20chief%20minister%20continues%2C%20minus%20any%20serious%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20big%20political%20decisions%20are%20taken%20in%20a%20vacuum%2C%20and%20it%20can%20be%20safely%20presumed%20that%20the%20decision%20by%20the%20BJD%20%E2%80%93%20long%20suspected%20to%20be%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20B-team%20%E2%80%93%20to%20extend%20support%20earlier%20this%20week%20came%20only%20after%20intense%20consultations%20and%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20they%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20holds%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20state%20assembly.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20state%20would%20elect%2021%20new%20members%20of%20parliament%20and%20vote%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20state%20government.%20It%20therefore%20gets%20more%20important%20for%20Patnaik%20who%20is%20eyeing%20another%20chief%20ministerial%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20never%20shown%20any%20interest%20in%20assuming%20a%20larger%20role%20at%20the%20national%20level%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20Modi%20or%20even%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20or%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%E2%80%93%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20politics%20has%20largely%20revolved%20around%20preserving%20his%20own%20position%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20For%20him%2C%20winning%20parliamentary%20seats%20is%20welcome%2C%20but%20only%20incidental.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20clearly%20being%20his%20priority%2C%20the%20BJD%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20support%20Modi%20in%20parliament%20serves%20his%20immediate%20political%20interest.%20It%20might%20have%20reinforced%20popular%20suspicion%20of%20BJD%20being%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20B-team%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20it%20does%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20credibility%20as%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20principal%20opposition%20party%20is%20significantly%20more.%20In%20popular%20perception%20%E2%80%93%20as%20reflected%20in%20opinion%20being%20currently%20voiced%20on%20social%20media%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20is%20non-serious%20about%20unseating%20Patnaik%20and%20is%20covertly%20in%20collusion%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20awkward%20for%20both%20parties%2C%20the%20unwritten%20proximity%20between%20the%20two%20promises%20political%20dividends%20for%20both.%20Patnaik%20remains%20popular%20and%20prospects%20of%20him%20being%20voted%20out%20next%20year%20look%20remote.%20An%20enfeebled%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20its%20credibility%20as%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20main%20opposition%20compromised%20and%20its%20cadre%20confused%20%E2%80%93%20makes%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20continuity%20as%20chief%20minister%20more%20certain.%20For%20all%20practical%20purposes%2C%20it%20could%20well%20be%20a%20friendly%20contest%20in%20Odisha%20the%20next%20time%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20too%20stands%20to%20gain.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20party%20has%20read%20the%20popular%20mood%20in%20Odisha%20and%20has%20come%20to%20accept%20that%20it%20has%20little%20realistic%20chance%20of%20defeating%20Patnaik.%20It%20has%20therefore%20set%20its%20sight%20on%20post-2024%20results%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20numbers%20in%20mind.%20Should%20it%20tally%20decline%20%E2%80%93%20as%20predicted%20by%20some%20political%20pundits%20%E2%80%93%20it%20would%20need%20to%20compensate%20for%20them.%20Patnaik%20with%20his%20MPs%20would%20come%20in%20handy%20then%20to%20ensure%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20majority%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20continuation%20in%20power.%20To%20give%20up%20on%20its%20ambitions%20in%20Odisha%20would%20only%20be%20a%20small%20price%20to%20be%20paid%20for%20achieving%20its%20larger%20political%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20which%20way%2C%20this%20suits%20Patnaik.%20Though%20professing%20to%20be%20equidistant%20from%20polarising%20political%20combinations%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20and%20the%20newly%20formed%20INDIA%2C%20Patnaik%20has%20always%20sided%20with%20whoever%20happened%20to%20be%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%20%E2%80%93%20right%20from%20AB%20Vajpayee%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh%20to%20Modi.%20Free%20of%20national%20ambitions%2C%20he%20had%20no%20political%20compulsion%20to%20oppose%20anyone.%20But%20being%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20one%20in%20power%20had%20benefits%3A%20it%20meant%20no%20CBI%20and%20ED%20and%20a%20relatively%20free%20run%20in%20his%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Patnaik%20prefers%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98covert%E2%80%99%20ally%20without%20giving%20up%20on%20his%20pretension%20of%20not%20being%20for%20or%20against%20any%20political%20group%20makes%20perfect%20sense.%20Joining%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20would%20invite%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20wrath.%20And%20officially%20siding%20with%20the%20BJP%20would%20open%20up%20the%20opposition%20space%20in%20Odisha%20for%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20Congress.%20He%20instead%20favours%20having%20a%20party%20he%20can%20influence%20as%20his%20principal%20opposition.%20To%20keep%20friends%20close%2C%20but%20enemies%20like%20the%20BJP%20closer%20seem%20to%20be%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20guiding%20principle.%20And%20he%20has%20been%20very%20successful%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERuben%20Banerjee%20is%20the%20former%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20Outlook%2C%20and%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fem%3ENaveen%20P