C%20the%20Taliban%20in%20Afghanistan%20have%20banned%20girls%20over%20the%20age%20of%2010%20from%20attending%20school%20in%20some%20provinces%20of%20the%20country%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fpersian%2Farticles%2Fcy6y1z5lg5yo%5C%22%3EBBC%20Persian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20officials%20from%20the%20Taliban-ruled%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20in%20the%20province%20of%20Ghazni%20have%20informed%20the%20heads%20of%20schools%20and%20short-term%20training%20programmes%20that%20%26quot%3Bgirls%20over%2010%20years%20old%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20study%20in%20primary%20schools%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20noted%20that%20in%20some%20regions%2C%20the%20'Ministry%20for%20Preaching%20and%20Guidance'%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20the%20Women's%20Affairs%20Ministry%2C%20requested%20the%20heads%20of%20girls'%20schools%20to%20send%20home%20any%20female%20students%20who%20were%20studying%20beyond%20third%20grade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20of%20class%20six%20from%20eastern%20Afghanistan%20told%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20that%20girls%20who%20are%20tall%20and%20over%2010%20years%20old%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Taliban%20officials%20announced%20a%20ban%20on%20women%20from%20educational%20institutes%20and%20it%20drew%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20foreign%20governments%20and%20the%20United%20Nations.%20%26quot%3BYou%20all%20are%20informed%20to%20immediately%20implement%20the%20mentioned%20order%20of%20suspending%20education%20of%20females%20until%20further%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20Minister%20for%20Higher%20Education%20Neda%20Mohammad%20Nadeem%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20issued%20to%20all%20government%20and%20private%20universities%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Taliban%20enforced%20the%20restriction%2C%20claiming%20that%20female%20students%20disregarded%20a%20stringent%20dress%20code%20and%20a%20necessity%20to%20be%20accompanied%20to%20and%20from%20university%20campuses%20by%20a%20male%20relative.%20The%20majority%20of%20colleges%20and%20universities%20had%20already%20implemented%20gender-specific%20entrances%2C%20classrooms%20and%20policies%20permitting%20only%20older%20men%20or%20women%20professors%20to%20teach%20female%20students%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20ban%20is%20one%20of%20many%20restrictions%20placed%20on%20women%20since%20the%20Taliban%20regime%20retook%20control%20in%20August%202021.%20Women%20in%20the%20country%20have%20also%20been%20banned%20from%20going%20to%20parks%2C%20gyms%2C%20fairs%2C%20salons%20and%20must%20cover%20themselves%20in%20public.%20Many%20have%20also%20been%20removed%20from%20their%20government%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691304240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fduj1c23_taliban_625x300_06_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaliban-ban-girls-from-studying-beyond-class-3-report-4273481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women%20in%20the%20country%20have%20also%20been%20banned%20from%20going%20to%20parks%2C%20gyms%2C%20fairs%2C%20salons%20and%20must%20cover%20themselves%20in%20public.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaliban-ban-girls-from-studying-beyond-class-3-report-4273481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaliban-ban-girls-from-studying-beyond-class-3-report-4273481%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftaliban-ban-girls-from-studying-beyond-class-3-report-4273481%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adah%20Sharma%20updates%20fans%20on%20having%20hive%3A%20Know%20details%22%2C%22conte