%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20will%20challenge%20the%20verdict%20in%20a%20higher%20court.%20The%20charges%20against%20me%20are%20politically%20motivated%2C%20as%20a%20majority%20of%20witnesses%20have%20testified%20that%20I%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20place%20mentioned%20in%20the%20police%20charge%20she%20et.%20The%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20government%20was%20in%20power%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20when%20the%20case%20was%20registered.%20A%20number%20of%20fabricated%20cases%20were%20being%20lodged%20against%20me%20at%20that%20time%20and%20this%20was%20one%20among%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Katheria%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying%20after%20the%20judgement%20was%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20judgement%20Katheria%20has%20been%20convicted%20in%20the%20case%20under%20IPC%20sections%20147%20(rioting)%20and%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt).%20The%20court%20said%20that%20his%20sentence%20would%20be%20extended%20by%20three%20months%20if%20the%20accused%20does%20not%20deposit%20the%20fine%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20client%20is%20innocent.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20the%20case%20to%20a%20higher%20court%20and%20will%20continue%20our%20legal%20efforts%20till%20he%20is%20proven%20not%20guilty%2C%E2%80%9D%20Katheria%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Devendra%20Singh%20said.%20The%20prosecution%20lawyer%20B%20M%20Kushwaha%20claimed%20that%20the%20case%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccrystal%20clear%E2%80%9D%20from%20day%20one%20.%E2%80%9D%20We%20are%20surprised%20why%20it%20dragged%20on%20over%20so%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kushwaha%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatheria%20has%20earlier%20served%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Agra%20twice%20before%20being%20elected%20from%20Etawah%20and%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20due%20to%20his%20conviction%20in