oners%20is%20worked%20out%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20latest%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20for%20Industrial%20Workers%20(CPI-IW)%20brought%20out%20by%20the%20Labour%20Bureau%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Labour%20Bureau%20is%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20Labour%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20PTI%2C%20All%20India%20Railwaymen%20Federation%20General%20Secretary%20Shiva%20Gopal%20Mishra%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20CPI-IW%20for%20June%202023%20was%20released%20on%20July%2031%2C%202023.%20We%20are%20demanding%20a%20four%20percentage%20point%20hike%20in%20dearness%20allowance.%20But%20the%20dearness%20allowance%20hike%20works%20out%20to%20be%20a%20little%20over%20three%20percentage%20points.%20The%20government%20does%20not%20factor%20in%20hiking%20DA%20beyond%20the%20decimal%20point.%20Thus%20DA%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20increased%20by%20three%20percentage%20points%20to%2045%20per%20cent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20explained%20that%20the%20expenditure%20department%20of%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20will%20formulate%20a%20proposal%20to%20hike%20DA%20along%20with%20its%20revenue%20implication%20and%20will%20put%20up%20the%20proposal%20before%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20for%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DA%20hike%20will%20be%20effective%20from%20July%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20over%20one%20crore%20central%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20are%20getting%20a%2042%20per%20cent%20dearness%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20revision%20in%20DA%20was%20done%20on%20March%2024%2C%202023%2C%20and%20was%20effective%20from%20January%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20increased%20DA%20by%20four%20percentage%20points%20to%2042%20per%20cent%20based%20on%20the%20percentage%20increase%20in%20the%2012%20monthly%20average%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20for%20the%20period%20ending%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DA%20is%20provided%20to%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20to%20compensate%20them%20for%20rising%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20increases%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%20and%20is%20reflected%20through%20CPI-IW.%20The%20allowance%20is%20revised%20periodically%20twice%20a%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691302860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F1nhc0dig_indian-currency-notes_625x300_22_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fda-hike-centre-likely-to-hike-dearness-allowance-to-45-for-over-1-crore-employees-4273445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Central%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20the%20dearness%20allowance%20(DA)%20for%20its%20over%20one%20crore%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20by%20three%20percentage%20points%20to%2045%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20existing%2042%20per%20cent%20as%20per%20the%20agreed%20formula%20for%20the%20purpose.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fda-hike-centre-likely-to-hike-dearness-allowance-to-45-for-over-1-crore-employees-4273445%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fda-hike-centre-likely-to-hike-dearness-allowance-to-45-for-over-1-crore-employees-4273445%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fda-hike-centre-likely-to-hike-dearness-allowance-to-45-for-over-1-crore-employees-4273445%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pics%3A%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20Tests%20Weapons%2C%20Briefs%20Soldiers%20At%20North%20Korea%20Factories%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20gave%20field%20guidance%20at%20major%20weapons%20factories%20between%20Thursday%20and%20Saturday%20including%20product