ational%2Fmirwaiz-umar-farooq-four-other-kashmiri-leaders-sign-bonds-to-secure-release%2Farticle29462227.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mirwaiz%20had%20signed%20a%20bond%20to%20secure%20his%20release%20from%20house%20arrest%20along%20with%20two%20leaders%20from%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20one%20leader%20each%20from%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20and%20Peoples%20Conference.%20The%20bond%2C%20reportedly%20signed%20under%20Section%20107%20of%20the%20CrPC%2C%20prohibited%20Mirwaiz%20and%20others%20from%20making%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20speeches%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20had%20rejected%20the%20claim%20that%20he%20signed%20a%20bond%20to%20secure%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20Mirwaiz%20has%20consistently%20criticised%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20policies%20and%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20his%20media%20statements%2C%20while%20calling%20for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20prisoners%20who%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20are%20presently%20languishing%20in%20different%20jails%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hurriyat%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20continue%20to%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20and%20interests%20of%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20advocate%20dialogue%2C%20good%20neighbourly%20relations%2C%20peaceful%20coexistence%20and%20brotherhood%20among%20communities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJailing%20Kashmiri%20political%20leadership%2C%20cadres%2C%20activists%20%E2%80%A6..%20as%20a%20means%20of%20establishing%20peace%20and%20an%20approach%20to%20problem%20solving%20is%20the%20way%20of%20the%20current%20dispensation.%20What%20is%20to%20be%20seen%20is%20how%20long%20this%20approach%20is%20followed%20and%20implemented%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Hurriyat%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20influential%20separatist%20leader%2C%20Mirwaiz%20was%20also%20part%20of%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20leaders%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20bilateral%20talks%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20over%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%20The%20delegation%20also%20met%20the%20then%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20L%20.K.%20Advani%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20suffered%20a%20setback%20in%202009%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20and%2C%20back%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20moderates%20were%20grilled%20by%20the%20hawks%20in%20the%20Hurriyat%20led%20by%20Syed%20Ali%20Geelani%20for%20participating%20in%20India-Pakistan%20rapprochement%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20beefed%20up%20on%20August%205%2C%20political%20leaders%20under%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20was%20beefed%20up%20across%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20Saturday%2C%20which%20marked%20the%20fourth%20anniversary%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20president%20and%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PDP%20chief%20had%20planned%20to%20lead%20a%20rally%20against%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20But%20the%20party%20said%20that%20besides%20Mehbooba%2C%20some%20of%20its%20senior%20leaders%2C%20such%20as%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20ministers%20Naeem%20Akhtar%20and%20A.R.%20Veeri%20among%20others%2C%20were%20either%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20or%20detained%20at%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20led%20by%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20also%20alleged%20that%20its%20party%20office%20in%20Srinagar%20was%20%E2%80%9Clocked%20down%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20authorities.%E2%80%9CTrue%20to%20form%20and%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20clampdown%20on%20mainstream%