ppen%20to%20any%20mother.%20For%20a%20new%20mother%2C%20when%20you%20get%20to%20know%20that...I%20got%20to%20know%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20me%20having%20a%20baby%20that%20our%20baby%20is%20born%20with%20two%20holes%20in%20her%20heart.%20I%20thought%20I'll%20not%20share%20this%2C%20but%20I'm%20sharing%20this%20because%20I%20feel%20that%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20mothers%2C%20who%20helped%20me%20in%20this%20journey%2C%20and%20it%20was%20very%20difficult%20to%20find%20those%20mothers...%20%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fon-bipasha-basus-pic-with-daughter-devi-a-mishti-comment-from-dad-karan-singh-grover-4163241%5C%22%3EBipasha%20Basu%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20that%20Devi%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20VSD%20%5Bventricular%20septal%20defect%5D.%20The%20actress%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20%5BBipasha%20and%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover%5D%20didn't%20even%20understand%20what%20a%20VSD%20is.%20It%20is%20a%20ventricular%20septal%20defect...We%20went%20through%20a%20crazy%20period.%20We%20didn't%20discuss%20this%20with%20our%20family%2C%20we%20both%20were%20in%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20blur.%20We%20wanted%20to%20celebrate%20but%20we%20were%20a%20little%20numb%2C%20me%20and%20Karan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20surgery%20for%20it%20and%20she%20and%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover%20prepared%20themselves%2C%20Bipasha%20Basu%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20five%20months%20have%20been%20very%20difficult%20for%20us.%20But%20Devi%20has%20been%20fabulous%20from%20day%20one.%20We%20were%20told%20that%20every%20month%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20a%20scan%20to%20know%20if%20it's%20healing%20on%20its%20own.%20But%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20large%20hole%20that%20she%20had%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20it%20was%20doubtful%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20go%20through%20surgery.%20And%20the%20surgery%20is%20best%20done%2C%20when%20the%20child%20is%20three-months-old.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBipasha%20Basu%20also%20added%20that%20Karan%20Singh%20Grover%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20ready%E2%80%9D%20for%20Devi's%20surgery.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20third%20month%20when%20we%20went%20for%20the%20scan%2C%20I%20pretty%20much%20did%20all%20the%20research%2C%20met%20surgeons%2C%20had%20been%20to%20hospitals%2C%20spoken%20to%20doctors%2C%20and%20I%20was%20kind%20of%20ready%2C%20Karan%20was%20not%20ready.%20I%20knew%20that%20she%20had%20to%20be%20okay%20and%20I%20knew%20that%20she%20will%20be%20okay.%20And%20she%20is%20okay%20now.%20But%20the%20tough%20decision%20was%20to%20get%20your%20child%20operated%20at%20the%20right%20place%20and%20at%20the%20right%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBipasha%20Basu%20told%20Neha%20Dhupia%20that%20Devi%20was%20in%20surgery%20for%20six%20hours.%20Bipasha%20added%20that%20she%20didn't%20sleep%20for%20%E2%80%9C40%20days%20and%2040%20nights.%20I%20am%20not%20lying.%20I%20swear%20on%20God.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBipasha%20Basu%20also%20gave%20fans%20an%20update%20on%20Devi's%20health.%20She%20said%20that%20their%20daughter%20is%20fine%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvkrydttATm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvkrydttATm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvkrydttATm%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C