20had%20highlighted%20how%20Mizoram%20and%20Meghalaya%20were%20carved%20out%20of%20Assam%2C%20underscoring%20the%20possibility%20of%20similar%20reorganisation%20of%20states%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F23120850%2FScreenshot-2019-11-23-at-12.08.35-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F23120850%2FScreenshot-2019-11-23-at-12.08.35-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F23120850%2FScreenshot-2019-11-23-at-12.08.35-PM-300x142.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F23120850%2FScreenshot-2019-11-23-at-12.08.35-PM-1024x484.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-415392%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20coming%20of%20India%2C%20Burma%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20were%20under%20one%20administration%20more%20or%20less%20but%20the%20British%20divided%20Mizoram%20into%20India%20and%20Burma%20and%20India%20and%20East%20Pakistan.%20Then%2C%20even%20inside%20India%2C%20the%20Mizos%20were%20still%20divided%20into%20different%20regions%20administratively%2C%20so%20when%20the%20MNF%20was%20founded%20by%20Mr.%20Laldenga%20on%20October%2022%2C%201961%2C%20the%20main%20target%20was%20unification%20of%20all%20the%20Mizo%20inhabited%20areas%20into%20a%20single%20administrative%20unit%E2%80%A6that%20was%20the%20main%20target%20of%20the%20founding%20fathers%20of%20the%20MNF%20but%20of%20course%2C%20the%20Myanmar%20side%20and%20now%20the%20Bangladesh%20side%2C%20since%20it%20is%20(they%20are)%20a%20foreign%20country%20we%20cannot%20say%20anything%20but%20within%20India%2C%20since%20it%20has%20happened%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20one%20state%20can%20be%20divided%20to%20form%20two%2C%20three%20states%20(sic)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zoramthanga%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAlthough%20the%20issue%20of%20unification%20has%20remained%20dormant%20since%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20peace%20accord%20in%201986%2C%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%20has%20allowed%20MNF%20to%20bring%20the%20latent%20issue%20to%20the%20fore%20once%20again.%20It%20should%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20Mizoram%2C%20under%20the%20MNF%20government%2C%20has%20taken%20in%20several%20Kukis%20who%20are%20fleeing%20persecution%20in%20their%20home%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWith%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Mizoram%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20ruling%20MNF%20has%20been%20under%20severe%20criticism%20over%20its%20alleged%20failure%20to%20fulfill%20the%20promises%20it%20made%20to%20the%20people%20in%20its%20manifesto.%20The%20move%20to%20provide%20shelter%20and%20support%20to%20Kukis%20has%20provided%20MNF%20with%20much-need%20positive%20public%20opinion%20among%20the%20electorate%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EEarly%20this%20week%2C%20a%20report%20comparing%20chief%20minister%20Zoramthanga%20himself%20with%20his%20Manipur%20counterpart%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%20On%20his%20official%20Instagram%20account%2C%20Zoramthanga%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20Kuki%20Zo%20youth%20who%20was%20arrested%20after%20he%20criticised%20Singh%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20and%20was%20later%20killed%20allegedly%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20jail.%20In%20the%20caption%2C%20Zoramthanga%20wrote%20that%20such%20an%20incident%20will%20never%20happen%20in%20Mizoram.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20further%20write%20that%20while%20Singh%20would%20arrest%20people%20for%20speaking%20against%20him%2C%20he%20would%20not%2C%20because%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20that%20type%20of%20leader%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EA%20political%20stunt%20by%20MNF%2C%20says%20opposition%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EWhat%20needs%20to%20be%20highlighted%20here%20is%20that%20despite%20the%20MNF%E2%80%99s%20heightened%20outreach%20on%20the%20Zo%20unification%20issue%2C%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Mizoram%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20it%20may%20not%20cut%20ice%20with%20the%20people%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%20Several%20opposition%20leaders%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20in%20Aizawl%20said%20that%20the%20MNF%20will%20have%20little%20to%20gain%20from%20its%20call%20for%20Zo%20unification%2C%20as%20it%20has%20failed%20in%20performing%20its%20responsibilities%20within%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Congress%20party%2C%20Lallianchhunga%2C%20believes%20the%20MNF%20is%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20political%20narrative%20in%20their%20favour%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9Csentimental%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEthnic%20cleansing%20is%20just%20something%20MNF%20has%20come%20up%20with%20to%20build%20a%20political%20narrative%20in%20their%20favour.%20The%20real%20issue%20in%20Manipur%20is%20the%20total%20silence%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20burning%20of%20churches.%20It%20is%20about%20religious%20issues%2C%20Hindu%20versus%20minority%20religions%2C%20especially%20Christians.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20other%20BJP%20national%20leaders%20have%20not%20addressed%20this%20yet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20issue%20will%20be%20resolved%20soon%20but%20the%20religious%20issue%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Cliving%20political%20issue%20as%20long%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20state%20level%2C%20especially%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ELallianchhunga%20further%20criticised%20the%20MNF%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20have%20ignored%20the%20major%20crisis%20in%20Mizoram%20such%20as%20the%20financial%20crisis%20and%20healthcare%20crisis%20that%20the%20state%20is%20facing.%20He%20also%20held%20MNF%20indirectly%20responsible%20for%20the%20suppression%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20in%20India%20because%20of%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fzoramthanga-on-ucc-and-manipur-violence%5C%22%3EMizoram%20CM%20Decries%20UCC%2C%20Rejects%20Accusation%20of%20%E2%80%98Meddling%E2%80%99%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Affairs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20afraid%20to%20leave%20the%20NDA%20and%20NEDA%20(North%20East%20Democratic%20Alliance)%2C%20because%20they%20still%20seek%20financial%20resources%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20They%20may%20also%20seek%20financial%20assistance%20for%20their%20election%20campaign.%20It%20is%20an%20open%20secret%20that%20the%20MNF%20had%20got%20financial%20assistance%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20partners%20in%20the%202018%20elections.%20This%20time%20around%20too%20they%20hope%20for%20getting%20financial%20resources%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20partners.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOn%20August%203%2C%20state%20Congress%20president%20Lalsawta%20upped%20the%20ante%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20gave%20a%20call%20to%20all%20political%20parties%2C%20NGOs%2C%20and%20churches%20in%20the%20state%20to%20%E2%80%9Cform%20a%20unified%20front%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D.%20He%20particularly%20underlined%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20policies%20%E2%80%9Cto%20suppress%20and%20eliminate%20the%20religious%20practice%20and%20cultures%20of%20the%20minorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EKenneth%20L%20Chawngthu%2C%20vice-president%20of%20Zoram%20People%E2%80%99s%20Movement%20(ZPM)%2C%20also%20echoed%20the%20same%20sentiment%20as%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Lallianchhunga.%20Chawngthu%E2%80%99s%20party%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20reason%20why%20this%20issue%20should%20benefit%20the%20MNF%20party%2C%20instead%2C%20it%20will%20defame%20them.%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20hold%20a%20direct%20face-to-face%20meeting%20with%20the%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this.%20He%20should%20go%20and%20meet%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20person.%20Also%2C%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20It%20is%20at%20times%20like%20these%20when%20they%20should%20make%20use%20of%20their%20alliance.%20Instead%2C%20they%20have%20built%20a%20bad%20reputation%20(for%20the%20party)%20for%20having%20failed%20to%20take%20action%20despite%20being%20alliance%20partners%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Reunification%20of%20the%20Zo%20people%20has%20been%20our%20party%20policy%20too%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%2C%20so%20it%20does%20not%20serve%20any%20advantage%20for%20the%20MNF%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20goal%20of%20every%20party%20in%20Mizoram%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chawngthu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMizoram%20BJP%20president%20Vanlalhmuaka%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20MNF%2C%20like%20many%20other%20parties%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpoliticise%20the%20issue%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20is%20politicising%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20except%20the%20BJP.%20Every%20political%20party%20is%20doing%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EVanlalhmuaka%20said%20he%20believes%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20MNF%20to%20unify%20the%20Zo%20people%20will%20go%20in%20vain%2C%20as%20it%20has%20still%20failed%20to%20uphold%20its%20duty%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Mizoram.%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20they%20have%20to%20think%20about%20the%20development%20of%20Mizoram%20first.%20They%20promise%20three%20lakhs%20per%20family%20(as%20a%20poll%20promise)%20and%20a%20flyover%20(in%20Aizawl)%20but%20they%20have%20failed%20to%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20J.%20Doungel%2C%20a%20well-known%20political%20analyst%20and%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%20at%20Mizoram%20University%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20Zo%20unification%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20politicisation%20but%20rather%20a%20common%20concern%20for%20the%20unification%20of%20people%20of%20the%20same%20ethnic%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20politicising%20the%20issue%2C%20all%20parties%20in%20Mizoram%20will%20have%20to%20finally%20care%20for%20their%20brothers%2C%20who%20related%20by%20bloodline.%20Therefore%2C%20all%20political%20parties%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%2C%20advocate%20Zo%20Unification.%20These%20parties%20propagate%20the%20slogan%20of%20Zo%20unification%20because%20they%20would%20like%20to%20explicitly%20show%20to%20the%20public%20that%20they%20stand%20for%20the%20unification%20of%20the%20Zo%20ethnic%20group.%20Since%20all%20political%20parties%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate%20to%20single%20out%20the%20MNF%20party%20for%20raising%20the%20issue.%20To%20my%20mind%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20politicisation%20of%20the%20issue%20but%20dealing%20with%20an%20ethnic%20issue%20on%20a%20political%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EDoungel%20said%20while%20the%20issue%20might%20impact%20the%20elections%2C%20as%20the%20voters%20would%20judge%20how%20the%20government%20is%20handling%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20ethnic%20factor%20would%20finally%20take%20a%20larger%20space%20than%20any%20party%20politicising%20it%20for%20its%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMNF%20has%20said%20Zo%20unification%20is%20something%20they%20included%20in%20its%20manifesto%20since%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20party%20with%20effect%20from%20October%2028%2C%201961%2C%20and%20that%20it%20is%20being%20continued%20till%20today%2C%20which%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20call%20it%20to%20be%20false%20though.%20The%20reason%20being%20%E2%80%98unification%20of%20all%20Zo%20inhabited%20territories%20under%20a%20single%20administrative%20unit%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20slogan%20of%20the%20party%20from%20the%20time%20MNF%20was%20formed.%20It%20may%20have%20a%20certain%20political%20advantage%20over%20it%2C%20but%20it%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20is%20not%20an%20issue%20MNF%20newly%20introduced%20into%20its%20agenda%20because%20of%20the%20current%20events%20in%20Manipur.%20It%20is%20only%20reviving%20it%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20continuation%20of%20its%20original%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691290955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12222305%2FIMG_0744-scaled-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmizoram-ahead-of-polls-mnfs-renewed-call-for-zo-unification-creates-political-flutter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20Kuki-Meitei%20face-off%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20Manipur%2C%20the%20emotional%20appeal%20for%20the%20unification%20of%20the%20Mizo-Zo%20community%20spread%20across%20the%20northeast%20has%20grown%20manifold.%20Although%20the%20issue%20has%20been%20dormant%20for%20decades%2C%20the%20ruling%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20has%20once%20again%20brought%20it%20to%20the%20fore.%22%2C%22author%