me%20Democratic%20donor%2C%20would%20not%20say%20how%20much%20money%20he%20lent%20Thomas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20fulfilled%20a%20dream%20by%20purchasing%20a%20luxury%20recreational%20vehicle%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclarence-thomas-can-essentially-do-whatever-he-wants-scotus-impeachment-2023-4%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Justice%20Clarence%20Thomas%3C%2Fa%3E%20received%20financial%20help%20from%20a%20surprising%20source%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20Saturday%3A%20a%20healthcare%20executive%20who%20would%20go%20on%2C%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20to%20donate%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20Thomas%2C%20who%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court%20eight%20years%20earlier%2C%20paid%20%24267%2C230%20for%20a%20Prevost%20Marathon%20RV%2C%20according%20to%20a%20title%20for%20the%20vehicle%20obtained%20by%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20since%2C%20Thomas%20has%20used%20the%2040-foot%20behemoth%20to%20tour%20the%20country%20and%20visit%20luxury%20resorts.%20In%20remarks%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Historical%20Society%2C%20Thomas%20said%20he%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Ginni%20%E2%80%94%20a%20right-wing%20activist%20who%20worked%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election%20%E2%80%94%20visited%2023%20states%20in%20the%20RV%20just%20over%20the%20summer%20of%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Thomas%20has%20never%20disclosed%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20vehicle%20was%20financed%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20Anthony%20Welters%2C%20a%20former%20executive%20at%20UnitedHealthCare%20who%20worked%20alongside%20Thomas%20in%20the%20Reagan%20administration.%20Welters'%20wife%2C%20Beatrice%2C%20served%20as%20an%20ambassador%20under%20Obama%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensecrets.org%2Fnews%2F2013%2F10%2Fkey-figure-at-unitedhealth-group-was-major-obama-donor%2F%5C%22%3Eto%20whom%20the%20couple%20donated%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20%24200%2C000%20and%20%24500%2C000%20during%20the%202008%20presidential%20campaign%20and%20another%20%24100%2C000%20for%20his%202009%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20comes%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fclarence-thomas-scotus-undisclosed-luxury-travel-gifts-crow%5C%22%3Ereporting%20from%20ProPublica%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20that%20Thomas%20has%20accepted%20gifts%20valued%20at%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20from%20another%20friend%2C%20Republican%20donor%20Harlan%20Crow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Times%2C%20Welters%20said%20he%20had%20provided%20Thomas%20a%20loan%20so%20he%20could%20buy%20the%20RV.%20He%20also%20provided%20a%20copy%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Blien%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20shows%20the%20loan%20was%20%26quot%3Bsatisfied%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Welters%20refused%20to%20say%20how%20much%20money%20he%20had%20lent%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20justice%2C%20nor%20on%20what%20terms.%20And%20while%20he%20said%20the%20loan%20was%20satisfied%2C%20that%20does%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20it%20was%20paid%20off%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20whether%20it%20should%20have%20been%20disclosed%20as%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20revelation%20comes%20amid%20a%20push%20to%20impose%20new%20ethics%20requirements%20on%20Supreme%20Court%20justices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20adopt%20the%20same%20code%20of%20ethics%20as%20every%20other%20federal%20judge%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20Sen.%20Dick%20Durbin%2C%20an%20Illinois%20Democrat%20who%20has%20sponsored%20new%20ethics%20legislation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fwashington-post-live%2F2023%2F07%2F13%2Fsen-richard-durbin-supreme-court-ethics-legislation%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%20last%20month%3C%2