embering%20a%20Doctor%2C%20Healer%20and%20a%20Remarkable%20Son%20of%20Magadh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05174757%2Fimage-1197.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Sunday%20(August%206)%20when%20a%20group%20of%20people%20assemble%20to%20remember%20Dr%20Farasat%20Hussain%2C%20in%20%E2%80%98Renaissance%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20aptly%20named%20Cultural%20Centre%20in%20Gaya%2C%20set%20up%20by%20his%20lifelong%20friend%2C%20noted%20litterateur%20Sanjay%20Sahay%20and%20his%20wife%20Durba%20Sahay%2C%20the%20inter-faith%20gathering%20will%20be%20much%20more%20than%20a%20tribute%20to%20him.%20They%20will%20of%20course%20meet%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20good%20doctor%20who%20died%20on%20July%2028%20at%20the%20age%20of%2071%20in%20Delhi.%20But%20the%20meeting%20will%20embody%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20Dr%20Hussain%E2%80%99s%20life%20which%20was%20dedicated%20to%20bridging%20divides%20and%20building%20relationships.%20Be%20it%20religious%2C%20caste%20and%20class%2C%20there%20was%20not%20one%20single%20divide%20he%20had%20not%20jumped%20across.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20will%20be%20very%20personal%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20but%20it%20will%20also%20be%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20India%20he%20inhabited%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20where%20he%20was%20proud%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20doctor%2C%20live%20his%20life%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3EMagadh%20ka%20baashinda%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Bihari%2C%20an%20Indian%2C%20and%20all%20in%20all%2C%20a%20lively%20human%20being.%20But%20it%20will%20also%20be%20a%20necessary%20reminder%20in%20these%20vicious%20and%20polarised%20times%20of%20people%20who%20with%20their%20singular%20focus%20on%20humanitarian%20work%20are%20the%20secret%20sauce%20of%20what%20keeps%20or%20certainly%20kept%20India%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Chhapra%20district%20in%201952%2C%20Dr%20Hussain%20made%20Gaya%20his%20home%20soon%20after%20he%20completed%20his%20post-graduation%20in%20Orthopaedic%20Surgery%20at%20Government%20Medical%20College%2C%20Ranchi%20in%201983.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20young%20doctor%2C%20he%20would%20kick-start%20his%20Rajdoot%20motorcycle%20and%20ride%20off%20to%20remote%20villages%20across%20Bihar%20to%20attend%20to%20emergencies.%20A%20pioneer%20in%20polio%20corrective%20surgeries%20in%20Bihar%2C%20he%20conducted%20scores%20of%20special%20camps%20where%20he%20performed%20more%20than%203%2C000%20polio%20surgeries%20for%20poor%20children%20when%20he%20started%20his%20work%20here%20decades%20ago.%20He%20even%20conducted%20Caesarean%20sections%20when%20a%20gynaecologist%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20state%20where%20public%20health%20was%20never%20really%20a%20thing%2C%20doctors%20like%20Farasat%20Hussain%20were%20the%20system.%20He%20was%20anyway%20an%20exceptional%20surgeon%20who%20had%20multiple%20opportunities%20and%20offers%20to%20make%20a%20career%20in%20the%20lucrative%20corporate%20medical%20sector%2C%20but%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20consider%20it.%20He%20stayed%20in%20Gaya%20where%20he%20mixed%20his%20practice%20as%20a%20doctor%20with%20large-scale%20social%20work%2C%20community%20building%20and%20helped%20initiate%20a%20multi-faith%20effort%20to%20ensure%20communal%20harmony%20across%20the%20Magadh%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20people%20there%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20skilful%20surgeon%20and%20an%20efficient%20clinician%2C%20he%20was%20also%20a%20psychologist.%20His%20unique%20sense%20of%20humour%2C%20they%20suspected%2C%20was%20part%20of%20his%20treatment%20plan%20for%20a%20patient.%20Dr%20Hussain%20didn%E2%80%99t%20merely%20look%20at%20the%20disease%20of%20his%20patients%2C%20he%20treated%20the%20person.%20In%20a%20place%20where%20health%20infrastructure%20had%20crumbled%20in%20the%20decades%20of%20the%2080s%20and%2090s%2C%20he%20was%20an%20address%20for%20the%20sick%20where%20they%20knew%20they%20would%20surely%20get%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20upliftment%20of%20the%20disabled%20population%2C%20who%20remember%20him%20as%20a%20mentor%20and%20benefactor%20for%20helping%20them%20with%20their%20livelihood.%20Several%20disabled%20people%20travelled%20from%20across%20the%20region%2C%20despite%20difficulties%2C%20and%20joined%20his%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Bihar%20honoured%20Dr%20Hussain%20for%20his%20work.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20he%20was%20national%20president%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Sports%20Medicine%20of%20India.%20He%20was%20honoured%20for%20his%20contribution%20to%20promote%20sports%20among%20disabled%20people%2C%20especially%20polio%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20was%20closely%20associated%20with%20Arpan%2C%20an%20organisation%20of%20disabled%20people%20in%20Gaya%2C%20where%20he%20was%20instrumental%20in%20motivating%20disabled%20youngsters%20to%20participate%20in%20sports%20and%20other%20activities%20to%20turn%20their%20physical%20challenges%20into%20opportunities%20that%20helped%20them%20move%20away%20from%20a%20life%20merely%20at%20the%20fringes%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20mentored%20Krishna%20Murari%2C%20who%20subsequently%20represented%20India%20at%20the%20sitting%20volleyball%20competition%20in%20the%20US.%20Several%20other%20disabled%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3Eyoungsters%20from%20the%20Magadh%20region%20also%20attended%20national%20sports%20events%20in%20cricket%2C%20volleyball%20and%20cycling.%20His%20focus%20on%20encouraging%20disabled%20youngsters%20to%20take%20up%20sports%20was%20to%20help%20in%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%20social%20fabric%2C%20not%20as%20dependents%2C%20but%20as%20equal%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20inter-faith%20dialogue%2C%20peace%20and%20harmony%20initiatives%20in%20the%20Magadh%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20those%20who%20attended%20his%20burial%20say%20that%20it%20aptly%20exhibited%20the%20fruits%20of%20his%20lifelong%20work%20to%20build%20bridges%20between%20communities.%20Buddhist%20monks%20came%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20him.%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20came%20and%20prayed%20for%20him.%20Several%20disabled%20men%20came%20for%20the%20first%20time%20into%20a%20graveyard%2C%20only%20to%20express%20their%20love%20for%20the%20departed.%20There%20were%20madrassa%20children%2C%20who%20were%20helped%20by%20him%20when%20their%20institution%20was%20in%20extreme%20financial%20distress.%20A%20befitting%20farewell%20to%20a%20man%20of%20all%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20had%20been%20closely%20involved%20with%20one%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20minority%20educational%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20Mirza%20Ghalib%20College%2C%20where%20he%20consistently%20promoted%20progressive%20and%20secular%20values.%20Mirza%20Ghalib%20would%20be%20proud%20of%20all%20that%20he%20upheld%20there.%20He%20was%20also%20involved%20with%20a%20number%20of%20charity%20organisations%2C%20such%20as%20an%20orphanage%20at%20Cherki%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades.%20This%20home%20for%20poor%2C%20underprivileged%20orphans%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20was%20an%20exceptional%20man%2C%20who%20stood%20out%20because%20he%20was%20so%20restless%20and%20always%20busy%2C%20working%2C%20helping%3B%20a%20doctor%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%20of%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20happened%20to%20meet%20him%20several%20times%2C%20and%20saw%20an%20adoring%20grandfather%20to%20a%20precocious%20and%20thoughtful%20Farris.%20His%20quiet%20charm%2C%20polished%20demeanour%20and%20contagious%20smile%20did%20not%20mean%20that%20he%20ever%20held%20back%20on%20his%20views.%20A%20man%20capable%20of%20sharp%20candour%20and%20an%20openness%20of%20the%20heart%2C%20he%20could%20surprise%20you%20with%20his%20diagnosis%20of%20the%20social%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Hussain%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20man%2C%20that%20if%20he%20himself%20were%20to%20read%20(or%20edit)%20this%20obituary%2C%20would%20frown%20and%20take%20serious%20umbrage%20at%20even%20a%20mention%20of%20his%20generosity%20as%20a%20doctor%2C%20friend%2C%20and%20human%20being.%20Good%20deeds%20were%20to%20be%20done%2C%20he%20believed%20firmly%2C%20and%20not%20to%20be%20remembered%20or%20recounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20at%20eternal%20rest%20now.%20But%20his%20life%20needs%20to%20be%20celebrated%20for%20how%20he%20lived%20it%20and%20how%20he%20wanted%20the%20world%20around%20him%20to%20be.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20nourish%20his%20legacy%2C%20intangible%20as%20it%20may%20seem.%20This%20is%20true%20today%20more%20than%20ever%20before%2C%20as%20we%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20even%20imagining%20living%20a%20harmonious%20life%20as%20a%20collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20very%20well%20that%20there%20was%20no%20magic%20pill%20to%20fix%20the%20social%20fabric%2C%20no%20ready%20%3Cem%3Erafoo.%3C%2Fem%3E%20But%20the%20good%20doc%20he%20was%2C%20he%20knew%20what%20it%20took%20to%20keep%20trying%20to%20get%20there%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20keeping%20all%20kinds%20of%20fevers%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERIP%2C%20Dr%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691240739000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05174757%2Fimage-1197.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdr-farasat-hussain-doctor-healer-obituary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Hussain%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20man%2C%20that%20if%20he%20himself%20were%20to%20read%20(or%20edit)%20this%20obituary%2C%20he%20would%20flinch%20at%20the%20mention%20of%20his%20generosity%20as%20a%20doctor%20or%20friend.%20Good%20deeds%20were%20to%20be%20done%2C%20he%20believed%2C%20not%20to%20be%20remembered%20or%20recounted.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdr-farasat-hussain-doctor-healer-obituary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Riots%20and%20Wrong%3A%20Communal%20Violence%20Raises%20Electoral%20Stakes%20but%20Who%20Gains%20From%20Polarisation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10130903%2F640px-thumbnail.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20every%20time%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20a%20fresh%20outpouring%20of%20violence%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20a%20statement%20by%20former%20police%20officer%20Vibhuti%20Rai%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CNo%20riot%20can%20last%20longer%20than%2024%20hours%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20trotted%20out%20to%20a%20wearied%20outrage.%20Now%20a%20platitude%2C%20it%20has%20been%20stripped%20of%20the%20horror%20of%20its%20meaning.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Rai%2C%20an%20IPS%20officer%20who%20worked%20through%20the%20riots%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20the%2080s%2C%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Finterview%2Fno-riot-can-last-more-24-hours-unless-state-wants-it-continue%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsabrangindia.in%2Finterview%2Fno-riot-can-last-more-24-hours-unless-state-wants-it-continue%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%201995%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20he%20had%20taken%20time%20off%20to%20conduct%20research%20on%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20police%20and%20those%20involved%20in%20communal%20violence.%20He%20found%20that%20while%20Hindus%20had%20a%20relationship%20of%20trust%20with%20the%20police%2C%20Muslims%20and%20Sikhs%20considered%20them%20enemies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20expressed%20grief%20at%20this%2C%20as%20the%20loss%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20state%20itself%2C%20but%20notably%2C%20put%20this%20down%20to%20a%20pervasive%20communal%20prejudice%20in%20the%20force%20that%20needed%20remediation.%20He%20insisted%20that%20no%20political%20party%20could%20demand%20that%20the%20police%20act%20in%20a%20communal%20fashion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERai%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20wrong%2C%20but%20what%20he%20failed%2C%20or%20refused%2C%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20when%20enough%20communal%20prejudice%20has%20been%20sown%20into%20the%20community%2C%20a%20politician%20would%20not%20have%20to%20ask%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20communal%20violence%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20electoral%20gains%20is%20hardly%20new%20as%20Babri%20and%20Godhra%20can%20attest%2C%20but%20we%20are%20now%20in%20a%20state%20where%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20exception%20in%20a%20larger%20culture%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esarkari%20(government)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20syncretism%2C%20but%20an%20expected%20feature%20of%20the%20political%20arena.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20at%20this%20juncture%20that%20we%20find%20Haryana%2C%20predictably%2C%20on%20fire.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBrij%20Mandal%20Jalabhishek%20Yatra%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20religious%20procession%2C%20was%20taken%20out%20by%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20on%20a%20route%20that%20was%20determined%20to%20go%20through%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20district%20which%20is%20predominantly%20populated%20by%20Muslims.%20Two%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20communal%20clashes%2C%20videos%20had%20gone%20viral%20featuring%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leaders%20Monu%20Manesar%20and%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20making%20inflammatory%20statements%20and%20calling%20for%20their%20supporters%20to%20assemble%20as%20a%20show%20of%20strength.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBot