n%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20amidst%20heavy%20security%2C%20with%20police%20deployed%20to%20turn%20away%20vehicles%20to%20prevent%20protesters%20reaching%20the%20site%2C%20the%20event%20went%20on%20as%20planned.%20To%20add%20insult%20to%20injury%2C%20the%20administration%20organised%20an%20event%20laying%20wreaths%20at%20the%20statue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20act%20of%20protest%2C%20around%2040%20BJP%20leaders%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fwhy-bjp-leaders-are-resigning-the-party-in-haryana-mihir-bhoj-statue-controversy-gujjar-rajput-manohar-lal-khattar-11690181585043.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresigned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20They%20included%20senior%20functionaries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20heads%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Morcha.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%2022%20villages%20in%20Haryana%20banned%20BJP%20leaders%20from%20entering%20their%20borders.%20The%20Rajput%20community%20gathered%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fcontroversy-erupts-over-unveiling-of-samrat-mihir-bhojs-statue-in-haryanas-kaithal-district%2Farticleshow%2F102043521.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECheeka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20town%20and%20burned%20an%20effigy%20of%20the%20government.%20By%20July%2025%2C%20that%20number%20had%20reached%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Ftension-over-statue-unveiling-rajput-community-resigns-from-bjp-and-rss-demands-removal-of-gurjar-from-statue-101690225512006.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E90%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20anti-BJP%20sentiment%20spreading%20like%20wildfire%20through%20the%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2030%2C%20the%20Rajputs%20held%20a%20%3Cem%3Em%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20i