3060400306_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERajputs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20with%206%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20they%20command%2017%20seats.%20The%20Gujjars%2C%20however%2C%20are%20influential%20in%2030-35%20seats%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20while%20they%20traditionally%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20vote%20swung%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcaste-calculations-in-rajasthan-and-why-pilot-matters-in-30-seats-123060400306_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2018%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20election%20when%20Sachin%20Pilot%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20leader%2C%20was%20sent%20up%20by%20Congress.%20That%20said%2C%20there%20is%20anti-Congress%20sentiment%20in%20the%20group%20now%20with%20their%20leader%20being%20denied%20the%20top%20position%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20Pilot%E2%80%99s%20public%20and%20vocal%20unhappiness%20on%20the%20subject.%20Both%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20are%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230710024918%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frajput-rajasthan-bhairon-singh-shekhawat-bjp-congress-8623357%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ematch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Rajput%20vote%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20took%20a%20cool%20100%20seats%20of%20the%20available%20200%2C%20with%20BJP%20under%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20stopping%20at%2073.%20This%20time%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20different%20%E2%80%93%20opinion%20polls%20show%20the%20BJP%20firmly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Frajasthan-election-2023-opinion-poll-prediction-ashok-gehlot-sachin-pilot-vasundhara-raje-bjp-congress-seats-tally-prediction%2F3191506%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eahead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20getting%20its%20infighting%20only%20recently%20under%20control%2C%20and%20an%20anticipated%20split%20of%20109-119%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%2078-88%20to%20Congress.%20If%20it%20came%20down%20to%20the%20line%2C%20it%20would%20be%20safer%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20alienate%20the%20Rajput%20vote%20over%20the%20Gujjar%2C%20but%20it%20would%20have%20ripple%20effects%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fbjp-overhauls-its-uttar-pradesh-unit%2Farticle66664913.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecultivating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20representation%20within%20the%20Brahmin%2C%20Rajput%20and%20non-Yadav%20OBCs%20as%20they%20cannot%20afford%20absolutely%20any%20uncertainty%20for%202024.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESet%20one%20problem%20to%20solve%20another%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20be%20extremely%20injudicious%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20ongoing%20Haryana%20riots%20have%20been%20deliberately%20manufactured%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20order%20to%20create%20conditions%20where%20unpleasant%20electoral%20outcomes%20can%20be%20avoided%20and%20a%20larger%20anti-Muslim%20threat%20can%20be%20mobilised%20to%20unite%20caste%20factionalism%20under%20the%20larger%20Hindutva%20umbrella.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20surely%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20used%20a%20larger%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpulwama-narendra-modi-bjp-2019-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20threat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20a%20way%20of%20shifting%20the%20dial%20on%20an%20election%20before%3F%20It%20would%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20be%20flirting%20with%20outright%20sedition%20to%20suggest%20that%20the%20creation%20of%20these%20conditions%20were%20a%20result%20of%20significant%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-satya-pal-malik-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecurity%20lapses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20by%20the%20state%20despite%20prior%20knowledge%20that%20should%20have%20prohibited%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2010%2F10%20seats%20from%20Haryana%2C%20and%2024%2F25%20out%20of%20Rajasthan%20(with%20a%20single%20seat%20going%20to%20an%20allied%20leader%20no%20longer%20affiliated%20with%20them).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20acquired%20four%20out%20of%2013%20in%20Punjab%20with%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20responsible%20for%20two%20of%20those%20before%20it%20ended%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20because%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20Punjab%20has%20issued%20a%20resounding%20anti-BJP%20knockout%20in%20its%202022%20state%20elections%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20winning%20a%20grand%20total%20of%20two%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20such%2C%20much%20is%20riding%20on%20Rajasthan%20and%20Haryana%20to%20maintain%20their%20full%20complements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-look-at-the-alliances-of-ruling-political-parties-ahead-of-the-2024-lok-sabha-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BPoonam%20Yadav%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20approximately%2045%25%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20specifically%20244%20out%20of%20the%20total%20543%20seats%2C%20are%20attributed%20to%2015%20states%20where%20neither%20the%20Congress%20nor%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power.%20With%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20steadily%20building%20a%20much%20larger%20coalition%20of%20major%20parties%2C%20these%20are%20seats%20where%20power%20can%20swing%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20favour%20more%20than%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2C%20as%20it%20stands%20with%20current%20alliances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20heavily%20emphasised%20that%20voters%20do%20not%20vote%20in%20general%20elections%20in%20the%20same%20way%20as%20they%20do%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20also%20evident%20at%20this%20juncture%20that%20the%20December%202023%20state%20elections%20have%20a%20lot%20riding%20on%20them%20in%20relation%20to%20how%202024%20will%20be%20perceived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20took%20a%20significant%20hit%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20Karnataka.%20To%20lose%20Rajasthan%20electorally%20and%20now%20Haryana%20emotively%20would%20take%20what%20is%20currently%20a%20tight%20race%2C%20into%20an%20active%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20has%20the%20BJP%20running%20nervous%2C%20given%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20parties%20has%20created%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-democracy-survival-complacency%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emultiplier%20effect%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20their%20favour.%20According%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAmitabh%20Tiwari%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20their%20vote%20share%20has%20gone%20up%20by%2010%25%2C%20whereas%20the%20factionalism%20running%20rampant%20in%20the%20BJP%20allies%20has%20brought%20theirs%20down.%20Of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20current%20303%20seats%2C%20there%20is%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-the-electoral-math-of-india-vs-nda-4240701%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclose%20fight%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20taking%20place%20in%2045.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%2035%20seats%20between%20Haryana%20and%20Rajasthan%20suddenly%20start%20to%20look%20a%20lot%20more%20important.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%2C%20there%20was%20a%20riot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20Haryana%20on%20fire%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20mobilisation%20of%20Hindutva%20militants%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20fake%20news%20factories%20amplifying%20narratives%20of%20Muslim%20violence%2C%20there%20is%20now%20a%20%E2%80%98bigger%20threat%E2%80%99%20than%20one%20of%20caste%20solidarity%20%E2%80%93%20not%20only%20has%20the%20wildfire%20momentum%20of%20the%20Rajput%20lobby%20been%20physically%20and%20digitally%20stopped%2C%20it%20will%20be%20unlikely%20to%20be%20revived%20given%20that%20Haryana%20will%20be%20tending%20to%20a%20different%20wound.%20It%20also%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20that%20the%20party%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20the%20optics%20of%20the%20Manipur%20gang%20rape%20viral%20video%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20neatly%20removed%20from%20the%20news%20cycle%20and%20replaced%20with%20bankable%20outrage%20and%20fury%20on%20the%20Haryana%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20refreshed%20the%20communal%20verve%20in%20the%20cow%20belt%2C%20where%20it%20has%20the%20most%20electoral%20returns%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20fresh%20so%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20start%20to%20remember%20they%20are%20unemployed%2C%20paying%20Rs%20160-a-kilo%20for%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20watching%20their%20taxes%20line%20Ambani%20pockets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20question%20still%20rises%2C%20out%20of%20sheer%20disbelief%3A%20surely%20all%20this%20could%20not%20be%20related%20to%20a%20statue%20of%20a%20man%20from%20the%209th%20century%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20which%20is%20%E2%80%93%20how%20much%20would%20you%20be%20willing%20to%20risk%20to%20win%20the%202024%20election%2C%20when%20the%20alternative%20is%20just%20to%20have%20a%20nice%20riot%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ