0procession%20was%20held%20by%20local%20leaders%20of%20the%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprotest%E2%80%9D%20the%20attack%20on%20their%20leaders%20in%20Nuh%20district.%20They%20were%20asked%20in%20advance%20to%20hold%20the%20march%20peacefully%20but%20the%20hate%20speech%20during%20the%20procession%20created%20tension%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20four%20people%20while%2012-15%20unidentified%20people%20have%20been%20booked%20under%20Sections%20505%20(inciting%20communal%20disharmony)%20and%20153-A%20(promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%20on%20grounds%20of%20religion)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20contents%20of%20the%20FIR%20are%20unknown%20as%20it%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20no%20arrest%20has%20been%20made%20yet%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20untoward%20incident%20after%20Wednesday%E2%80%99s%20religious%20procession%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20no%20exodus%20of%20people%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20was%20reported%20in%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SHO%20said%20that%20since%20the%20matter%20is%20sensitive%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20not%20uploaded%20to%20the%20website%20of%20the%20Haryana%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20incident%2C%20local%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20(SDM)%20Mohit%20Maharana%20also%20called%20a%20meeting%20with%20local%20Hindu%20leaders%20on%20Thursday%20to%20prevent%20any%20further%20flare%20up.%20Maharana%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChand%20Miyan%2C%20who%20is%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20local%20Dargah%20in%20Hansi%2C%20condemned%20the%20incident%20and%20said%20that%20such%20incidents%20should%20not%20happen%20as%20they%20result%20in%20disharmony.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20all%20communities%20in%20this%20town%20have%20lived%20in%20peace%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%2090%25%20of%20the%20visitors%20to%20the%20dargah%20are%20Hindus.%20We%20all%20must%20live%20in%20harmony%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20local%20Muslim%20population%20was%20worried%20after%20the%20boycott%20call%2C%20he%20said%20the%20situation%20reamins%20peaceful.%20The%20local%20police%20were%20very%20cooperative.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20provided%20security%20to%20places%20of%20our%20worship%20after%20the%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20similar%20incidents%20were%20reported%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20villages%20of%20Mahendragarh%20and%20Rewari%20districts%20have%20issued%20similar%20diktats%2C%20stating%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20allow%20vendors%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20enter%20their%20village.%20Ratan%20Singh%2C%20a%20sarpanch%20from%20Salarpur%20village%20in%20Mahendragarh%2C%20is%20quoted%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20entire%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sarpanch%20of%20Rewari%E2%80%99s%20Chimnawas%20village%20also%20echoed%20similar%20views.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20from%20the%20community%20roam%20around%20our%20village%20during%20daytime%20and%20then%20loot%20our%20village%20in%20night%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20memorandum%20will%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rewari%20deputy%20commissioner%20(DC)%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20Additional%20information%20was%20added%20to%20this%20article%20after%20it%20as%20published.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691236517000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05171614%2FScreenshot-2023-08-05-at-5.11.22-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-hisar-rally-hindutva-muslims-boycott-fir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20station%2