F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20shivering%20cold%20morning%20in%20Delhi%20on%20December%2019%2C%201947.%20Cold%20winds%20were%20blowing%20and%20there%20was%20no%20trace%20of%20the%20sun.%20The%20mood%20in%20Delhi%20was%20sombre%2C%20as%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20capital%20like%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20Pahar%20Ganj%20and%20Shahdara%20were%20in%20flames%20due%20to%20unabated%20communal%20violence%20despite%20the%20untiring%20efforts%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20Since%20his%20arrival%20at%20Shahdara%20Railway%20station%20on%20September%209%2C%201947%20from%20Calcutta%20%E2%80%93%20after%20controlling%20the%20riots%20there%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20again%20visiting%20the%20riot-torn%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20morning%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20at%20the%20Birla%20House%20at%20Tees%20January%20Marg.%20He%20was%20ready%20to%20visit%20Gurugaon%E2%80%99s%20Jesarah%20village%2C%20around%2055%20kilometres%20from%20Delhi.%20He%20had%20been%20asked%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20visit%20the%20region%20by%20respected%20Meo%20leader%20Ch.%20Yasin%20Khan.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20Punjab%20assembly%20and%20the%20Unionist%20Party%2C%20Khan%20met%20Gandhi%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20September%2020%2C%201947%20at%20Birla%20House%20and%20told%20him%20that%20hundreds%20of%20Muslims%20from%20the%20Mewat%20region%20were%20planning%20to%20leave%20for%20Pakistan%20because%20of%20the%20violence%20they%20faced%20in%20Alwar%20and%20Bharatpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20hearing%20this%20plea%2C%20Gandhi%20told%20Khan%20that%20he%20would%20visit%20Mewat%20soon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2019%2C%201947%2C%20his%20programme%20was%20conveyed%20to%20Khan%20and%20others.%20They%20made%20elaborate%20arrangements%20for%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20address%20at%20Jesarah%20village%20panchayat%20ground.%20Gandhi%20reached%20there%20before%2012%3A30%20pm.%20It%20would%20have%20taken%20around%20two%20hours%20to%20reach%20there%2C%20as%20roads%20beyond%20Dhaula%20Kuan%20were%20pathetic%20during%20those%20days.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EGopi%20Chand%20Bhargava%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Punjab%2C%20and%20a%20couple%20of%20others%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Harijan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2028%2C%201947%2C%20Gandhiji%20told%20the%20packed%20Jesarah%20panchayat%20ground%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20voice%20was%20not%20so%20powerful%20as%20it%20once%20used%20to%20be.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20whatever%20I%20said%20was%20acted%20upon.%20If%20I%20had%20the%20original%20power%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20should%20have%20found%20it%20necessary%20to%20migrate%20to%20Pakistan%20from%20India%20or%20a%20single%20Hindu%20or%20Sikh%20to%20leave%20his%20home%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20seek%20asylum%20in%20the%20Indian%20Union.%E2%80%9D%20The%20capacity%20crowd%20was%20listening%20to%20his%20address%20with%20full%20attention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGandhi%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20murder%2C%20arson%2C%20loot%2C%20abductions%2C%20forcible%20conversation%20were%20really%20barbaric.%E2%80%9D%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20gory%20incidents%20that%20rocked%20the%20country%20after%20India%E2%80%99s%20partition.%20Naturally%2C%20he%20was%20very%20sad%20about%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20and%20sounded%20helpless.%20A%2017-year-old%20boy%20was%20also%20there%20at%20Jesarah%20panchayat%20ground%20with%20his%20father%20and%20other%20family%20members.%20He%20later%20became%20Maulana%20Jameel%20Iliyasi%20and%20established%20the%20mosque%20on%20the%20capital%E2%80%99s%20Kasturba%20Gandhi%20Marg.%20Years%20later%2C%20his%20eyes%20become%20moist%20recalling%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20historic%20visit%20to%20Mewat.%20He%20believes%20that%20Mewat%20would%20remain%20indebted%20to%20the%20Mahatma%20for%20giving%20a%20helping%20hand%20when%20it%20was%20facing%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20trouble.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20589px)%2085vw%2C%20589px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06100652%2Ffacebook_1691237405979_7093563816848810014.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06100652%2Ffacebook_1691237405979_7093563816848810014.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06100652%2Ffacebook_1691237405979_7093563816848810014-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F06100652%2Ffacebook_1691237405979_7093563816848810014-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-666838%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22589%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20ground%20where%20Gandhi%20spoke.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Harijan%3C%2Fem%3E%20further%20reports%20that%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20feel%20happy%20if%20my%20words%20could%20bring%20some%20consolation%20to%20you%20in%20the%20distress.%E2%80%9D%20Referring%20to%20the%20Meo%20refugees%2C%20who%20had%20been%20driven%20out%20of%20Alwar%20and%20Bhartapur%20states%2C%20Gandhi%20remarked%20that%20he%20looked%20forward%20to%20the%20day%20when%20all%20enmities%20would%20be%20forgotten%20and%20hatred%20buried%20underground%20and%20all%20those%20who%20had%20driven%20away%20from%20their%20hearths%20and%20homes%20would%20return%20to%20them%20and%20resume%20their%20evocations%20in%20perfect%20security%20and%20peace%20as%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20he%20told%20all%20those%20planning%20to%20move%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20shun%20their%20decision.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20belongs%20to%20you%20and%20you%20belong%20to%20India.%E2%80%9D%20And%20Meos%20did%20not%20disappoint%20him.%20They%20decided%20to%20stay%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20India%20rather%20than%20move%20to%20Jinnah%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20address%2C%20Gandhi%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20told%20Meos%20were%20almost%20like%20criminal%20tribes.%20If%20the%20statement%20was%20correct%2C%20it%20called%20for%20an%20all%20out%20effort%20on%20their%20part%20to%20reform%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Surely%2C%20only%20a%20brave%20man%20like%20Gandhiji%20could%20have%20made%20this%20statement%20to%20them.%20After%20his%20address%20at%20Jesarah%2C%20he%20spent%20some%20time%20with%20Meo%20leaders%20at%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20home%20and%20had%20his%20vegetarian%20lunch%20there.%20As%20the%20cold%20conditions%20were%20becoming%20severe%2C%20the%20dhoti-clad%20Gandhi%20left%20for%20Delhi%20to%20attend%20his%20multifaith%20prayer%20meeting.%20There%20too%2C%20he%20discussed%20the%20Jesarah%20trip.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECut%20to%20now%3A%20No%20leader%20worth%20his%20salt%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Evisited%20Mewat%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20riots%20and%20destruction%20that%20have%20erupted%20there%20recently.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20school%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Gandhiji%20exists%20in%20Jesarah.%20Some%20village%20elders%20assemble%20there%20every%20year%20on%20December%2019%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F911290%2Fwhy-the-meo-muslims-in-mewat-remember-mahatma-gandhi-in-december-every-year%5C%22%3Ecommemorate%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20visit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVivek%20Shukla%20is%20a%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691233214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05162325%2FMahatma_Gandhi_at_Bhangi_sweepers_colony_New_Delhi.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22