ewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05145711%2FF1JX-vRaQAIJi2j.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20historic%20move%2C%20Rajasthan%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-minimum-income-law-has-provided-a-development-model-for-the-nation-gehlot%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520law%2520guarantees%2520125%2520days%2Ca%252015%2525%2520increment%2520every%2520year.%5C%22%3Epassed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill.%20Critics%20argue%20that%20it%20will%20pose%20huge%20fiscal%20challenges%20and%20therefore%20it%20may%20produce%20cosmetic%20changes%20only.%20It%20is%20argued%20that%20the%20already%20high%20state%20debt%20of%20about%2040%25%20of%20GSDP%20will%20further%20burgeon%20and%20put%20a%20burden%20on%20future%20generations.%20Given%20today%E2%80%99s%20competitive%20politics%2C%20other%20state%20governments%20will%20also%20be%20under%20pressure%20to%20follow%20suit%20before%20the%20coming%20assembly%20and%20national%20elections.%20Thus%2C%20the%20budgetary%20arithmetic%20of%20the%20country%20will%20deteriorate.%20Were%20similar%20arguments%20not%20advanced%20in%20the%20mid-2000s%20when%20rights%20like%20MGNREGS%20and%20the%20right%20to%20food%20were%20proposed%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20at%20the%20Centre%20feeling%20threatened%20has%20been%20derisively%20characterising%20such%20schemes%20as%20%3Cem%3Erevdis%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20freebies.%20Can%20all%20the%20schemes%20for%20public%20welfare%20be%20tarnished%20with%20the%20same%20brush%3F%20Different%20schemes%20serve%20diverse%20social%20purposes.%20Some%20of%20them%20provide%20public%20services%20while%20others%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20poor%20to%20survive.%20Schemes%20enabling%20good%20education%20and%20health%20are%20essential%20public%20services.%20Giving%20money%20to%20the%20unemployed%20or%20pension%20to%20the%20elderly%20and%20destitute%20provides%20them%20sustenance.%20Such%20schemes%20enable%20society%20to%20fulfil%20its%20constitutional%20obligation%20of%20the%20right%20to%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESchemes%20that%20give%20the%20voters%20cycles%2C%20gas%20cylinders%2C%20laptops%20and%20so%20on%20help%20the%20recipients%20ease%20their%20lives%20but%20are%20not%20essential.%20A%20cheap%20gas%20cylinder%20liberates%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20unhealthy%20smoky%20wood-fired%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20cycle%20for%20a%20girl%20child%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20her%20to%20attend%20school.%20A%20laptop%20may%20enable%20a%20child%20to%20learn%20better.%20But%2C%20such%20goods%20may%20not%20be%20the%20first%20choice%20for%20the%20family.%20If%20they%20had%20adequate%20income%2C%20they%20could%20prioritise%20what%20they%20needed%20most%20%E2%80%93%20not%20necessarily%20what%20is%20offered%20in%20election%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fgig-workers-first-major-victory-in-india-rajasthan-leads-the-way%5C%22%3EGig%20Workers%E2%80%99%20First%20Major%20Victory%20in%20India%3A%20Rajasthan%20Leads%20the%20Way%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInadequate%20trickle%20down%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncome%20is%20the%20key%20to%20people%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%20If%20they%20have%20adequate%20income%20to%20live%20a%20civilised%20existence%2C%20they%20would%20not%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20the%20government%20to%20give%20them%20things%20other%20than%20public%20services.%20To%20have%20an%20income%2C%20people%20need%20work%20in%20the%20market.%20Thus%2C%20employment%20is%20the%20key%20to%20the%20issue%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%20In%20the%20%E2%80%98Report%20on%20Employment%20and%20Unemployment%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20released%20in%20October%202022%2C%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20320%20million%20may%20have%20some%20proper%20work%2C%20280%20million%20do%20not%20have%20proper%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEffectively%2C%20those%20who%20have%20some%20proper%20income%20have%20to%20support%20three%20others%20in%20the%20family.%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20burden%20on%20those%20working%20and%20also%20results%20in%20family%20poverty.%20If%20the%20280%20million%20who%20do%20not%20have%20proper%20work%20in%20the%20market%20were%20to%20get%20work%2C%20family%20poverty%20would%20immediately%20decline%20%E2%80%93%20because%20then%20each%20working%20person%20would%20have%20to%20support%20only%20one%20other.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoverty%20and%20unemployment%20are%20not%20ordained%20by%20nature%20but%20are%20a%20result%20of%20national%20policies.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20copy%20Western%20modernity%2C%20India%20has%20since%20Independence%20pursued%20trickle-down%20policies%20based%20on%20top-down%20approach.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20well-off%20prospering%20with%20little%20trickling%20down%20to%20the%20marginalised.%20The%20top-down%20approach%20promoted%20modern%20industries%20and%20infrastructure%20that%20are%20mechanised%20and%20increasingly%20automated.%20These%20constitute%20the%20organised%20sector%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20which%20offers%20good%20jobs%20but%20only%20employs%206%25%20of%20the%20workers.%20The%20rest%20have%20to%20work%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20at%20low%20incomes.%20The%20result%20has%20been%20inadequate%20employment%20generation%20for%20the%20fast-expanding%20population%2C%20persistence%20of%20poverty%20and%20stress%20for%20the%20vast%20majority.%20Rajasthan%20is%20one%20of%20the%20states%20where%20such%20problems%20are%20evident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20marginalisation%20of%20the%20majority%20also%20results%20in%20the%20economy%20growing%20slowly.%20With%20the%20masses%20(94%25%20of%20the%20workforce)%20lacking%20adequate%20purchasing%20power%2C%20demand%20tends%20to%20remain%20low%20and%20so%20does%20the%20rate%20of%20growth.%20Only%20when%20exports%20do%20well%20or%20the%20government%20introduces%20rights-based%20programmes%20that%20growth%20gets%20a%20boost.%20The%20latter%20happened%20during%202004-09.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20prior%20to%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20in%202020%2C%20the%20quarterly%20rate%20of%20growth%20had%20dropped%20from%208%25%20to%203%25%20due%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20demonetisation%20and%20a%20structurally%20flawed%20GST%2C%20both%20of%20which%20severely%20impacted%20the%20unorganised%20sectors.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20official%20data%20does%20not%20capture%20this%20decline%20since%20it%20is%20largely%20based%20on%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20organised%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20brief%2C%20the%20actual%20situation%20of%20the%20marginalised%20is%20far%20worse%20than%20what%20the%20official%20data%20reflects.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill%20is%20timely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EProvisions%20of%20the%20Bill%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20immediately%20offer%20support%20where%20it%20is%20needed%20the%20most%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20unemployed%2C%20the%20elderly%20and%20the%20disabled.%20It%20provides%20for%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20additional%20entitlement%20of%2025%20days%20per%20rural%20family%20for%20work%20under%20MGNREGS.%20The%20additional%20funds%20required%20to%20be%20provided%20by%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E125%20days%20of%20work%20to%20one%20member%20of%20a%20family%20under%20an%20urban%20employment%20programme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20pension%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20all%20elderly%2C%20widowed%20and%20disabled%20persons.%20This%20is%20much%20more%20than%20what%20has%20been%20on%20offer%20till%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%20will%20be%20the%20first%20state%20in%20the%20country%20to%20enhance%20the%20legal%20entitlement%20under%20MGNREGS%20by%2025%20additional%20days.%20Also%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20state%20is%20by%20law%20guaranteeing%20a%20minimum%20pension%20which%20will%20rise%20by%2015%25%20annually%20(not%20just%20indexed%20to%20inflation).%20Critics%20argue%20that%20this%20provision%20is%20inadequate.%20Further%2C%20they%20argue%2C%20an%20urban%20employment%20scheme%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20implement%20and%20will%20lead%20to%20greater%20urbanisation.%20But%2C%20that%20is%20what%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20are%20pushing%20for.%20So%2C%20the%20critics%20are%20contradicting%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20provision%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20has%20been%20made%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20provisions%20in%20the%20Bill.%20This%20may%20be%20inadequate%20and%20allocations%20will%20have%20to%20be%20enhanced%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14083452%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14083452%2FUntitled-design-11.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14083452%2FUntitled-design-11-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14083452%2FUntitled-design-11-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640375%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20labourer%20at%20work%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Photo%3A%20Eric%20Parker%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-NC%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIs%20it%20fiscally%20profligate%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20critics%20argue%20that%20the%20proposals%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20swelling%20of%20the%20already%20high%20debt%20of%20the%20state%20and%20increase%20the%20interest%20burden%20on%20the%20budget%2C%20which%20will%20reduce%20the%20availability%20of%20funds%20for%20capital%20expenditure%20and%20other%20developmental%20activities.%20But%2C%20why%20is%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20poor%20not%20a%20developmental%20activity%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnytime%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor%20are%20announced%2C%20the%20pro-business%20lobby%20gets%20active%20and%20calls%20them%20fiscally%20profligate.%20When%20concessions%20and%20subsidies%20are%20announced%20for%20businesses%2C%20they%20are%20given%20the%20positive%20spin%20of%20%E2%80%98incentives%E2%80%99%20to%20promote%20business.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20they%20will%20generate%20work%20and%20incomes%2C%20which%20will%20boost%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20debate%20hinges%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20incentives%20for%20businesses%20will%20boost%20the%20economy%2C%20even%20if%20demand%20is%20short.%20Evidence%20is%20that%20it%20does%20not.%20Demand%20is%20crucial%20for%20better%20capacity%20utilisation%2C%20increased%20investment%20and%20higher%20growth%20rate%20and%20employment%20generation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20issues%20arise.%20Are%20resources%20available%20for%20funding%20such%20schemes%3F%20And%2C%20are%20there%20spin-offs%20of%20such%20schemes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFunds%20in%20the%20budget%20are%20fungible.%20They%20can%20be%20spent%20on%20any%20item%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20prioritisation%20in%20the%20budget%20%E2%80%93%20a%20political%20issue.%20If%20public%20services%20and%20employment%20are%20given%20a%20high%20priority%2C%20funds%20will%20become%20available.%20After%20all%2C%20poverty%20and%20unemployment%20are%20not%20naturally%20ordained.%20They%20are%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20economic%20policies%20determined%20by%20the%20ruling%20elite.%20Their%20priority%20is%20to%20grab%20resources%20for%20themselves%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20little%20for%20the%20marginalised.%20Further%2C%20unemployment%20benefits%20them%20by%20keeping%20wages%20down%20so%20that%20they%20get%20cheap%20labour%20for%20their%20homes%20and%20businesses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20brief%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20not%20of%20resource%20shortage%20but%20of%20political%20priority%20for%20the%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor.%20When%20votes%20matter%2C%20politicians%20propose%20such%20schemes.%20One%20policymaker%20from%20the%20World%20Bank%20stable%20suggested%20in%201993%20that%20the%20government%20can%20pursue%20anti-poor%20policies%20till%20mid-way%20to%20the%20next%20elections%20and%20after%20that%20cater%20to%20the%20poor.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20poor%20are%20enticed%20closer%20to%20the%20elections%20but%20no%20permanent%20solution%20to%20end%20their%20marginalisation%20is%20implemented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20issue%2C%20the%20spin-offs%20from%20the%20proposed%20schemes%20are%20obvious.%20Mass%20demand%20will%20increase%20and%20a%20better-trained%20and%20healthier%20workforce%20will%20be%20available%20for%20the%20economy.%20Consequently%2C%20people%20will%20lead%20a%20more%20civilised%20existence%20and%20become%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20demand%20rises%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20will%20also%20do%20better.%20Since%20most%20of%20the%20taxes%20are%20collected%20from%20the%20organised%20sector%2C%20whether%20direct%20taxes%20or%20indirect%20taxes%2C%20the%20government%20will%20get%20more%20revenue.%20Indirect%20taxes%20are%20regressive%20but%20most%20of%20the%20GST%20is%20collected%20from%20the%20organised%20sector.%20The%20unorganised%20sector%20is%20outside%20the%20pale%20of%20GST.%20In%20effect%2C%20the%20initial%20rise%20in%20the%20budgetary%20deficit%20will%20give%20way%20to%20a%20more%20balanced%20budget.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConclusion%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitical%20parties%20are%20likely%20to%20follow%20suit%20and%20the%20promises%20being%20made%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20will%20get%20generalised%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20with%20states%20likely%20to%20implement%20similar%20schemes.%20This%20was%20seen%20prior%20to%20the%202019%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20when%20state%20governments%20and%20the%20Centre%20vied%20with%20each%20other%20to%20initiate%20income%20support%20to%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20schemes%20are%20only%20implemented%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20expansion%20of%20demand%20in%20the%20state%20will%20leak%20out.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20its%20revenues%20would%20not%20rise%20sufficiently%20to%20cover%20the%20deficit%20over%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20above%2C%20poverty%20and%20unemployment%20are%20not%20naturally%20ordained%20but%20an%20outcome%20of%20the%20policies%20being%20pursued.%20So%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20not%20of%20shortage%20of%20resources%20but%20of%20lack%20of%20political%20will.%20The%20Rajasthan%20government%20has%20shown%20the%20will%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20coming%20elections%2C%20to%20help%20the%20marginalised%20in%20the%20long%20run%20by%20passing%20the%20Minimum%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Bill.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EArun%20Kumar%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Economy%20since%20Independence%3A%20Persisting%20Colonial%20Disruption%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Economy%E2%80%99s%20Greatest%20Crisis%3A%20Impact%20of%20Coronavirus%20and%20the%20Road%20Ahead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691228704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F05145711%2FF1JX-vRaQAIJi2j.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-minimum-guaranteed-income-bill-intent-marginalisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Critics%20argue%20that%20the%20Bill%20will%20pose%20huge%20fiscal%20challenges%20and%20therefore%20it%20may%20produce%20cosmetic%20changes%20only.%20But%20tackling%20poverty%20and%20unemployment%20requires%20political%20will.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-minimum-guaranteed-income-bill-intent-marginalisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RPF%20Cop%20Who%20Killed%20an%20Officer%2C%203%20Muslim%20Passengers%20on%20Train%20to%20Face%20Communal%20Discord%20Charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F28145254%2F13286908034_bb8f865649_h.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Government%20Railway%20Police%20(GRP)%20has%20decided%20to%20include%20provisions%20pertaining%20to%20inciting%20communal%20disharmony%20against%20RPF%20constable%20Chetan%20Singh%2C%20who%20killed%20three%20Muslim%20passengers%20and%20an%20assistant%20sub-inspector%2C%20on%20a%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20the%20Jaipur%20Mumbai%20Superfast%20Express%20train%20on%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20civilian%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Abdul%20Qadirbhai%20Mohammed%20Hussain%20Bhanpurwala%2C%20Akhtar%20Abbas%20Ali%2C%20and%20Sadar%20Mohammed%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20the%20agency%20is%20considering%20the%20communal%20aspects%20of%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20purported%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%