r%20her%2015%20year%20career%2C%20she%20often%20saw%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20families%20of%20the%20deceased.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20see%20wailing%20children%20and%20elderly%20next%20to%20their%20loved%20ones.%20They%20would%20not%20have%20sufficient%20money%20to%20perform%20the%20last%20rites%20and%20the%20authorities%20demanded%20a%20huge%20amount%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remembered%20how%20my%20husband%20%5Bwho%20lived%20back%20home%20in%20Odisha%5D%20would%20do%20this%20work%20without%20charging%20any%20amount.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20when%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20leg%20was%20fractured%20after%20slipping%20on%20a%20railway%20track%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20come%20back%20to%20her%20hometown.%20When%20no%20one%20from%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20non-profit%20Pradeep%20Sewa%20Trust%20was%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20job%20of%20cremating%20bodies%2C%20she%20stepped%20in%20and%20quit%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20receiving%20information%20from%20the%20GRP%2C%20Madhusmita%20drives%20to%20the%20spot%2C%20from%20where%20they%20lift%20the%20bodies.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fcremation-1691066277-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326202%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20receiving%20information%20from%20the%20GRP%2C%20Madhusmita%20drives%20to%20the%20spot%2C%20from%20where%20they%20lift%20the%20bodies.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20when%20the%20country%20was%20coping%20with%20the%20losses%20of%20loved%20ones%20amid%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20she%20cremated%20more%20than%20500%20unidentified%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227488%2Findia-unclaimed-bodies-burial-padma-shri-uttar-pradesh-inspiring-hero-shareef-chacha-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunclaimed%20bodies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20patients%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Bhubaneswar%20Municipality%20Corporation.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20cremated%20more%20than%201%2C500%20such%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoughly%20five%20months%20ago%2C%20Madhusmita%20was%20joined%20by%20Smita%2C%20Swagatika%2C%20and%20Snehanjali%20in%20the%20initiative.%20While%20Swagatika%20is%20a%20bank%20employee%20and%20Snehanjali%20is%20a%20journalist%20by%20profession%2C%20Smita%20runs%20a%20small%20shop%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20first%20day%20at%20work%2C%20Smita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20an%20elderly%20person%2C%20whose%20head%20was%20at%20one%20place%2C%20and%20body%20at%20another.%20His%20one%20hand%20laid%20half%20a%20kilometre%20away.%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20keep%20the%20body%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeing%20the%20body%20also%20triggered%20a%20devastating%20memory%20for%20the%2043-year-old%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20brother%20in%20an%20accident%2010%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20hardly%20know%20what%20exactly%20happened%20to%20him.%20We%20never%20got%20his%20body.%20He%20was%20just%2014.%20He%20was%20so%20young%2C%20but%20he%20always%20dreamt%20big%20things%20for%20me.%20He%20wanted%20to%20gift%20me%20a%20car%2C%E