20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20to%20spread%20awareness%20among%20people%20about%20the%20existence%20of%20Northeastern%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20toy%20created%20at%20Zankla%20Studio%20carries%20a%20narrative%20native%20to%20the%20tribe%20or%20is%20a%20representation%20of%20a%20prominent%20person%20from%20the%20tribe%2C%20such%20as%20Ada%20Lowdoom%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20traveller%2C%20Bodo%20Jwhwlao%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20Bodo%20fighter%2C%20Gowdang%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20princess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20pamphlet%20containing%20the%20story%20or%20tale%20of%20the%20fictional%20or%20real%20character%20that%20the%20toy%20is%20based%20on%2C%20explains%20Kirat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sole%20purpose%20of%20these%20toys%20is%20to%20generate%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20community.%20A%20lot%20of%20research%20and%20thought%20is%20put%20into%20creating%20each%20toy.%20We%20have%20so%20many%20lost%20stories%20and%20characters%20from%20folklore.%20We%20create%20our%20toys%20based%20on%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FClQTdf4A6Sy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FClQTdf4A6Sy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2