curriculum%20covers%20a%20two-year%20course%20in%20just%20one%20year.%20We%20teach%20the%20subjects%20in%20their%20native%20language%20to%20strengthen%20their%20understanding%20and%20also%20help%20them%20with%20the%20regional%20language%20used%20in%20the%20school%20they%20want%20to%20join.%20The%20training%20lasts%20for%20one%20or%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20children%20are%20bridged%20to%20their%20learning%20levels%2C%20they%20are%20mainstreamed%20in%20a%20government%20school.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20enrolling%20them%20in%20schools%2C%20we%20found%20that%20there%20are%20hardly%20enough%20teachers%20to%20manage%20hundreds%20of%20students.%20It%20was%20impractical%20for%20us%20to%20expect%20any%20kind%20of%20learning%20for%20our%20children.%20The%20students%20complained%20to%20us%20that%20nothing%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20schools.%20Having%20worked%20so%20hard%20to%20mainstream%20them%2C%20if%20they%20dropped%20out%2C%20then%20all%20efforts%20would%20go%20to%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20co-founder%20Manimakalai%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20that%20works%20towards%20the%20educational%20inclusion%20of%20out-of-school%20and%20marginalised%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-1-1690981239-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326081%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20that%20works%20towards%20the%20educational%20inclusion%20of%20out-of-school%20and%20marginalised%20children%20of%20migrant%20families.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202016%2C%20I%20finally%20found%20myself%20teaching%20in%20these%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20In%20these%20government%20schools%2C%20Gubbachi%20utilises%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F72957%2Fanita-kaul-ias-rte-act-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Nali%20Kali%E2%80%99%20scheme%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20means%20%E2%80%98joyful%20learning%E2%80%99%20in%20Kannada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20classes%20are%20full%20of%20activities.%20Regular%20subjects%20are%20taught%20through%20games%2C%20songs%2C%20colourful%20charts%2C%20educational%20toys%2C%20game%20boards%2C%20dice%2C%20flashcards%2C%20and%20storytelling.%20We%20also%20conduct%20weekly%20dance%20activities%20and%20sports%20classes%20twice%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manimakalai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20several%20government%20schools%20approached%20us%20to%20adopt%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20multi-grade%20and%20multi-level%20education%20program%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2053-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Gubbachi%20has%20established%20two%20centres%20to%20implement%20the%20bridge%20learning%20programme%20and%20works%20with%20nine%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171106%2Fbengaluru-govt-school-inspiring-hero-education-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egovernment%20schools%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20educate%20classes%201%E2%80%933%20through%20Nali%20Kali.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20give%20these%20children%20a%20good%20foundation%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20perform%20better%20in%20Class%204%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20they%20have%20associated%20with%20over%2060%20teachers%20to%20help%20them%20implement%20various%20programmes%20in%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20equitable%20learning%20for%20thousands%20for%20free%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20above%2010%20years%20of%20age%20or%20above%2C%20Gubbachi%20first%20enrols%20them%20in%20bridge%20learning%20and%20then%20mainstreams%20them%20in%20English%20medium%20schools%20for%20further%20education%2C%20informs%20Manimakalai.%20The%20organisation%20handholds%20its%20students%20throughout%20formal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fgubbachi-4-1690981344-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326088%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20has%20assisted%20more%20than%204%2C000%20migrant%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Vijay%20Kumar%20%3Cem%3E(name%20changed)%20%3C%2Fem%3Egot%20enrolled%20in%20Azim%20Premji%20University%20for%20a%20BA%20Honours%20(Economics)%20course%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Gubbachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2013%2C%20Vijay%20migrated%20from%20his%20home%20state%20Jharkhand%20for%20better%20schooling%20and%20to%20live%20with%20his%20father%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20house%20helper%20for%20a%20wealthy%20Bengaluru%20family.%20But%2C%20Vijay%20was%20denied%20admission%20to%20a%20local%20private%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20understand%20English%20and%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20other%20subjects%20like%20Maths.%20I%20left%20school%20after%20Class%205%2C%20so%20my%20basics%20were%20not%20clear.%20My%20Maths%20understanding%20was%20of%20Class%203%20level.%20So%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20I%20felt%20dejected%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20now%2018-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20learnt%20about%20Gubbachi%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20employer.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20non-profit%E2%80%99s%20programme%2C%20where%20he%20was%20trained%20to%20read%20and%20write%20English%20and%20understand%20Mathematics.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20the%20organisation%20helped%20him%20enrol%20for%20senior%20secondary%20schooling%20(Class%2010)%20at%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS)%2C%20a%20government-run%20%E2%80%9Copen%20school%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20explained%20concepts%20to%20me%20in%20my%20language%20and%20helped%20me%20read%20textbooks.%20They%20emphasised%20that%20memorising%20exact%20vocabulary%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20necessary%2C%20and%20I%20always%20wrote%20down%20what%20I%20understood.%20This%20approach%20m