uld%20achieve%20anything.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrent%20PHRA%20secretary%20Madhu%20Poplai%2C%20who%20has%20been%20carrying%20forward%20the%20mission%20since%20Sumi%20left%20in%202004%2C%20concurs.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20those%20days%2C%20we%20used%20to%20visit%20our%20ward%20office%20and%20police%20station%20regularly%2C%20like%20how%20people%20visit%20temples.%20We%20would%20drop%20our%20children%20at%20school%20and%20then%20proceed%20together.%E2%80%9D%20Madhu%20has%20been%20a%20PHRA%20member%20since%20its%20inception%2C%20and%20has%20been%20holding%20the%20post%20of%20either%20Chairman%20or%20Secretary%20for%20the%20last%2016%20years%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20in%20groups%20is%20effective%2C%20says%20Sumi.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20working%20for%20a%20public%20cause%2C%20always%20work%20and%20move%20around%20in%20groups%2C%20more%20so%20when%20meeting%20officials.%20Keep%20on%20knocking%20their%20doors%20till%20they%20hear%20you.%20Involve%20housewives%20and%20retired%20men.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20funding%2C%20PHRA%20originally%20requested%20residents%20to%20contribute%20Rs%20360%20per%20flat%20per%20annum%2C%20and%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20bungalow%20per%20annum.%20Today%2C%20they%20have%20raised%20the%20amount%20to%20Rs%20900%20and%20Rs%202%2C500%20respectively.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20people%20thought%20we%20were%20collecting%20money%20to%20have%20kitty%20parties%20or%20for%20our%20household%20expenses.%20They%20were%20not%20convinced%20that%20a%20few%20women%20like%20us%20would%20achieve%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sanchali%20Sarkar%2C%20present%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20team%20that%20went%20house%20to%20house%20to%20gather%20funds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20managing%20committee%20with%2021%20members%20(18%20women%20and%203%20men)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288533%2Fhow-to-volunteer-programmes-