s%20Start%20Businesses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EK%20Priya%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20residents%20of%20Tirupati%E2%80%99s%20Tirumala%20Nagar%2C%20sold%20flowers%20on%20a%20pushcart%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%20They%20have%20two%20two%20boys%2C%20one%20in%20Class%2010%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Class%209.%20To%20save%20up%20for%20their%20college%20education%2C%20Priya%20wanted%20to%20rent%20a%20shop%20to%20sell%20flowers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20aware%20that%20someone%20like%20me%20could%20get%20a%20loan.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20who%20to%20approach%20or%20how%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Barathi%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20milk%20business%20from%20Tirupati%2C%20who%20recalls%20having%20to%20jump%20through%20hoops%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20run%20a%20milk%20shop%20and%20needed%20a%20loan%20to%20expand.%20I%20had%20to%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20get%20my%20loan%20sanctioned%20earlier.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20there%20is%20a%20large%20gender%20gap%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20access%20to%20credit.%20A%202022%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Finance%20Corporation%20(IFC)%20%3C%2Fem%3Eestimates%20a%20Rs%20836%20billion%20credit%20demand%20by%20women-owned%20very%20small%20enterprises.%20Meanwhile%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3EProtium%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereport%20further%20states%20that%20there%20is%20a%C2%A0%20credit%20gap%20of%20%24158%20billion%20for%20women-led%20businesses%20as%20a%20whole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Barathi%20and%20Priya%2C%20India%20P2P%2C%20a%20peer-to-peer%20lending%20platform%20run%20by%20Mumbai-based%20entrepreneur%20Neha%20Juneja%20has%20been%20a%20boon.%20Barathi%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20pamphlet%20and%20I%20called%20them.%20An%20officer%20came%2C%20and%20after%20verifying%20the%20details%2C%20the%20loan%20was%20disbursed%20in%20a%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Similar%20was%20the%20case%20of%20Priya%2C%20who%20availed%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20in%20March%202023%2C%20and%20was%20successfully%20able%20to%20set%20up%20her%20flower%20shop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20says%20that%20her%20introduction%20to%20microfinance%20happened%20when%20she%20was%20working%20with%20rural%20women%20at%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%2C%20which%20manufactures%20biomass%20cook%20stoves.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20travelled%20to%20several%20villages%20and%20saw%20the%20thriving%20self-help%20groups%20(SHG)%20credit%20culture.%20I%20discovered%20that%20they%20are%20a%20great%20asset%20class%20and%20pay%20back%20loans%20on%20time.%20I%20also%20found%20that%20they%20are%20starved%20of%20credit%20as%20conventional%20investors%20can%E2%80%99t%20make%20up%20their%20mind%20that%20rural%20women%20are%20income%20generators%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neha%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EClosing%20the%20credit%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20660px)%20100vw%2C%20660px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neha%20Juneja%20started%20India%20P2P%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239.jpeg%20660w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-300x205.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-500x341.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fneha2-1690548239-150x102.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325613%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeha%20Juneja%20started%20India%20P2P%20in%202021%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20launched%20India%20P2P%20in%202021.%20The%20company%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20attempt%20to%20unlock%20more%20capital%20for%20women%20borrowers%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20for%20businesses%20or%20purchase%20of%20productive%20assets%20like%20washing%20machines%20or%20refrigerators%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%20By%20eliminating%20the%20middleman%2C%20i.e%2C%20the%20bank%2C%20this%20platform%20gets%20the%20capital%20for%20these%20loans%20by%20letting%20investors%20invest%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20they%20have%20built%20a%20technology%20platform%20that%20enables%20risk%20and%20portfolio%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20retail%20investors%20invest%20directly%20in%20the%20women%20borrowers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20technology%20platform%3C%2Fa%3E%20ends%20up%20reducing%20credit%20cost%20for%20the%20borrower.%20The%20platform%20splits%20your%20investment%20across%2010%20borrowers%20from%2010%20geographies%2C%20mitigating%20the%20risk.%20It%20has%20various%20parameters%20to%20split%20your%20capital%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20built%20an%20app%20for%20borrowers%2C%20agents%2C%20and%20an%20underwriting%20module.%20Neha%20says%20that%20they%20are%20able%20to%20give%20about%2015-16%20per%20cent%20return%20to%20their%2018%2C000%20investors%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%2010%2C000%20loans.%20India%20P2P%20partners%20with%20last%20mile%20organisations%20like%20Seva%20Mandir%20and%20UNDP%20in%20pockets%20across%20the%20country.%20These%20regions%20include%20Nagaland%2C%20all%20five%20southern%20states%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20women%20everywhere%20are%20able%20to%20access%20credit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20NGOs%20and%20microfinance%20institutions%20(MFIs).%20Most%20loans%20are%20given%20to%20women%20who%20are%20part%20of%20SHGs%2C%20which%20is%20a%20powerful%20structure%20for%20accountability.%20They%20attend%20the%20weekly%20group%20meetings%20of%20SHGs%20to%20ensure%20that%20those%20who%20need%20loans%20are%20given%20loans.%20Our%20loan%20officers%20visit%20the%20borrower%E2%80%99s%20place%20of%20work%20for%20due%20diligence.%20Once%20they%20are%20satisfied%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20disbursed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20loans%20disbursed%20fall%20between%20Rs%2040%2C000%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20on%20an%20average.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIndian%20women%20have%20higher%20credit%20scores%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22India%20P2P%20caters%20majorly%20to%20women%20borrowers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-1690548462-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fwomen-india-p2p-169054846